Kind: captions

00:00:08.342 --> 00:00:10.043 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Hayakawa groans]

00:00:10.177 --> 00:00:11.579 position:24% line:89% align:start
Life is so unfair.

00:00:11.713 --> 00:00:13.280 position:24% line:89% align:start
Why am I stuck here

00:00:13.413 --> 00:00:16.283 position:16% line:83% align:start
instead of getting pruney
in a hot spring?

00:00:16.518 --> 00:00:18.285 position:24% line:83% align:start
-We just got back.
-[Hayakawa sulking]

00:00:18.418 --> 00:00:20.287 position:27% line:83% align:start
Why didn't you go
for New Year's?

00:00:20.420 --> 00:00:23.257 position:7% line:83% align:start
Because between visiting family
and holiday obligations

00:00:23.390 --> 00:00:24.592 position:19% line:89% align:start
I didn't have any time

00:00:24.726 --> 00:00:26.460 position:27% line:83% align:start
-for a vacation!
-[SHINOZAKI] Calm down.

00:00:26.594 --> 00:00:28.462 position:27% line:83% align:start
You can't tell me
recharging at a hot spring

00:00:28.596 --> 00:00:30.732 position:5% line:89% align:start
doesn't sound like a great idea.

00:00:30.899 --> 00:00:33.968 position:30% line:83% align:start
Being outside,
surrounded by nature's beauty.

00:00:34.101 --> 00:00:35.369 position:19% line:89% align:start
All the while serenaded

00:00:35.503 --> 00:00:37.539 position:27% line:83% align:start
by chirping birds
and babbling brooks

00:00:37.672 --> 00:00:40.374 position:19% line:83% align:start
as perfectly hot water
melts your problems away.

00:00:40.508 --> 00:00:43.545 position:24% line:83% align:start
Sign me up for this
office worker's paradise please!

00:00:43.678 --> 00:00:45.713 position:19% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI] Well, she's
definitely got Senpai

00:00:45.847 --> 00:00:47.080 position:33% line:89% align:start
on her side!

00:00:47.347 --> 00:00:50.217 position:19% line:83% align:start
Just think, we all need
some TLC for the soul!

00:00:50.350 --> 00:00:51.653 position:27% line:89% align:start
That's for sure.

00:00:51.786 --> 00:00:53.788 position:24% line:83% align:start
I get exactly where
you're coming from.

00:00:54.388 --> 00:00:57.124 position:19% line:83% align:start
I bet they'd even have
a local kitty to play with.

00:00:57.324 --> 00:00:58.793 position:5% line:89% align:start
I can't think of a better escape

00:00:58.927 --> 00:01:01.729 position:7% line:83% align:start
from this harsh concrete jungle
that we all live in.

00:01:01.863 --> 00:01:03.932 position:21% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI] Not good.
Senpai's trapped herself

00:01:04.064 --> 00:01:05.533 position:13% line:89% align:start
on her own fantasy island!

00:01:05.667 --> 00:01:07.635 position:21% line:83% align:start
Hey, why don't we go
at the end of the month?

00:01:07.769 --> 00:01:09.704 position:27% line:83% align:start
We'll use our PTO
and play hooky!

00:01:09.837 --> 00:01:11.973 position:10% line:83% align:start
-Sounds like an awesome idea!
-[giggle]

00:01:12.105 --> 00:01:13.608 position:10% line:89% align:start
You wanna join in on the fun?

00:01:14.408 --> 00:01:16.511 position:10% line:83% align:start
Wouldn't it be kind of weird
for me to go though?

00:01:16.644 --> 00:01:18.312 position:24% line:83% align:start
So, you don't want
to see your Senpai

00:01:18.445 --> 00:01:20.180 position:21% line:89% align:start
fresh outta the bath?

00:01:21.348 --> 00:01:24.418 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'm your Senpai,
fresh outta the bath.

00:01:24.719 --> 00:01:26.888 position:38% line:83% align:start
It's not,
not something I'd like to see.

00:01:27.021 --> 00:01:30.123 position:13% line:83% align:start
But if I take time off now,
I might fall behind.

00:01:30.324 --> 00:01:31.859 position:16% line:83% align:start
-[AKINA] I say go for it.
-Huh!

00:01:32.292 --> 00:01:33.460 position:21% line:89% align:start
[SHINOZAKI] Manager!

00:01:33.595 --> 00:01:35.462 position:19% line:83% align:start
We are in a slow period
right now.

00:01:35.597 --> 00:01:38.298 position:13% line:83% align:start
The point of paid vacation
is to use it up after all.

00:01:38.432 --> 00:01:40.467 position:13% line:83% align:start
-You're the best, Manager!
-You're the best, Manager!

00:01:40.602 --> 00:01:43.938 position:13% line:83% align:start
In that case, why don't you
come with us too?

00:01:44.237 --> 00:01:45.439 position:38% line:89% align:start
You sure?

00:01:45.573 --> 00:01:47.407 position:33% line:83% align:start
It'd be weird
if I was the only guy.

00:01:47.609 --> 00:01:50.344 position:27% line:83% align:start
I love that idea.
Let's all go together.

00:01:50.477 --> 00:01:53.081 position:21% line:83% align:start
It wouldn't be as fun
without the entire gang there.

00:01:53.213 --> 00:01:54.916 position:19% line:89% align:start
Don't you think so too?

00:01:55.083 --> 00:01:57.518 position:38% line:83% align:start
I guess.
If he really wants to.

00:01:58.086 --> 00:02:01.355 position:13% line:83% align:start
All of us at a hot spring.
Huh?

00:02:01.689 --> 00:02:02.824 position:35% line:89% align:start
Oh, Senpai.

00:02:02.957 --> 00:02:04.491 position:30% line:89% align:start
Oh, Shinozaki.

00:02:05.026 --> 00:02:06.027 position:38% line:89% align:start
Hayakawa.

00:02:06.159 --> 00:02:07.729 position:35% line:89% align:start
Shinozaki.

00:02:08.395 --> 00:02:09.496 position:30% line:89% align:start
Well, come on!

00:02:09.631 --> 00:02:11.666 position:33% line:83% align:start
-Um, Katase?
-Huh?

00:02:11.799 --> 00:02:13.601 position:33% line:89% align:start
[all chuckle]

00:02:14.167 --> 00:02:17.038 position:21% line:83% align:start
-I wouldn't miss this
for the whole world! -Quit it!

00:02:17.170 --> 00:02:20.407 position:21% line:83% align:start
If you keep that up,
then you can just stay at home!

00:03:55.036 --> 00:03:57.905 position:24% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI] This place
is even more charming in person!

00:03:58.139 --> 00:03:59.607 position:7% line:89% align:start
And just think on any other day

00:03:59.741 --> 00:04:01.642 position:19% line:83% align:start
we would all be chained
to our desks!

00:04:01.776 --> 00:04:05.146 position:13% line:83% align:start
-[HAYAKAWA] Thank you, PTO!
-While you do that,

00:04:05.278 --> 00:04:06.514 position:21% line:83% align:start
-I'll go check us in.
-Oh.

00:04:06.647 --> 00:04:08.415 position:24% line:89% align:start
Thank you, manager.

00:04:08.850 --> 00:04:10.618 position:7% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI] It was nice of you
to drive us up here

00:04:10.752 --> 00:04:12.352 position:24% line:83% align:start
on top of handling
the reservations.

00:04:12.486 --> 00:04:13.688 position:41% line:83% align:start
[AKINA]
Don't sweat it.

00:04:13.821 --> 00:04:15.857 position:33% line:83% align:start
I enjoy doing
this kind of stuff.

00:04:15.990 --> 00:04:18.458 position:30% line:83% align:start
And I did share
driving duties with Katase.

00:04:18.593 --> 00:04:19.794 position:21% line:83% align:start
I was kinda surprised
to find out

00:04:19.927 --> 00:04:21.829 position:19% line:83% align:start
-that she could drive.
-[chuckles]

00:04:21.963 --> 00:04:24.198 position:35% line:83% align:start
It makes me
wanna get my license.

00:04:24.331 --> 00:04:26.067 position:47% line:83% align:start
Oh.
Good thinking.

00:04:26.200 --> 00:04:27.367 position:10% line:89% align:start
That way she can ride shotgun

00:04:27.502 --> 00:04:29.237 position:24% line:83% align:start
while you drive us
on our next trip.

00:04:29.369 --> 00:04:31.371 position:13% line:89% align:start
I mean, that's one reason.

00:04:31.506 --> 00:04:33.007 position:27% line:83% align:start
-[Shiori screams]
-[gasps]

00:04:33.141 --> 00:04:34.441 position:16% line:89% align:start
That was Senpai's voice!

00:04:34.575 --> 00:04:36.911 position:33% line:83% align:start
Wait, is this
a murder hot spring?

00:04:37.044 --> 00:04:38.179 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:04:38.311 --> 00:04:39.914 position:19% line:89% align:start
I'll save you, Senpai!

00:04:40.047 --> 00:04:43.618 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Meow.
-[meowing]

00:04:43.918 --> 00:04:47.188 position:24% line:83% align:start
I've died and gone
to fluffy wuffy heaven.

00:04:47.354 --> 00:04:49.422 position:30% line:83% align:start
Thankfully it's
a figurative death.

00:04:49.557 --> 00:04:52.093 position:16% line:83% align:start
You know, cats are a sign
of a good inn.

00:04:52.226 --> 00:04:53.795 position:16% line:89% align:start
And you picked a winner!

00:04:53.961 --> 00:04:58.465 position:19% line:83% align:start
Hello, widdle kitties.
Who wants hugs?

00:05:00.034 --> 00:05:01.936 position:38% line:89% align:start
[crying]

00:05:02.069 --> 00:05:04.005 position:10% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI] That was painful
to watch.

00:05:04.172 --> 00:05:06.707 position:19% line:83% align:start
Maybe they're too alike
for them to be interested?

00:05:06.841 --> 00:05:08.643 position:7% line:89% align:start
[SHINOZAKI] Senpai's not a cat!

00:05:08.776 --> 00:05:11.612 position:21% line:83% align:start
-[crying] -She's got
some catlike qualities

00:05:11.746 --> 00:05:14.549 position:16% line:83% align:start
but that's not something
they could pick up on, right?

00:05:15.216 --> 00:05:16.851 position:10% line:89% align:start
What do you think, Hayakawa?

00:05:16.984 --> 00:05:18.886 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'm a bit purr-occupied.

00:05:19.020 --> 00:05:20.221 position:27% line:89% align:start
A human cat tree!

00:05:20.353 --> 00:05:23.524 position:24% line:83% align:start
Is your entire body
made out of catnip or something?

00:05:24.859 --> 00:05:26.493 position:33% line:89% align:start
[chattering]

00:05:26.994 --> 00:05:30.198 position:19% line:83% align:start
I was already impressed
that they had a hot spring pool

00:05:30.463 --> 00:05:32.099 position:21% line:89% align:start
but this is gigantic!

00:05:32.233 --> 00:05:33.734 position:27% line:89% align:start
Isn't this great?

00:05:33.868 --> 00:05:36.304 position:13% line:83% align:start
It's year-round summer fun!
Let's make the most of it!

00:05:36.804 --> 00:05:39.140 position:7% line:83% align:start
I never thought I'd see Senpai
in a swimsuit,

00:05:39.273 --> 00:05:42.844 position:16% line:83% align:start
let alone during winter.
I gotta keep it together.

00:05:44.679 --> 00:05:46.914 position:24% line:83% align:start
I wonder what kind
of suit she has?

00:05:47.048 --> 00:05:48.749 position:21% line:89% align:start
Maybe something cute?

00:05:51.052 --> 00:05:53.888 position:24% line:83% align:start
Or maybe something
on the classy side?

00:05:54.989 --> 00:05:56.524 position:35% line:89% align:start
Or maybe...

00:05:56.824 --> 00:05:59.327 position:19% line:83% align:start
[HAYAKAWA] Oh. Katase!
Over here!

00:05:59.627 --> 00:06:01.963 position:7% line:89% align:start
Sorry to keep you all waiting.

00:06:09.103 --> 00:06:11.873 position:7% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI] I was not expecting
something this mature!

00:06:12.006 --> 00:06:14.275 position:38% line:83% align:start
Not good!
I can't let any dirty thoughts

00:06:14.407 --> 00:06:15.676 position:21% line:89% align:start
creep out of my head!

00:06:15.810 --> 00:06:17.745 position:24% line:83% align:start
I gotta stay calm,
she's still my Senpai!

00:06:17.879 --> 00:06:21.115 position:13% line:83% align:start
I'll just go with a casual,
nonspecific compliment.

00:06:21.381 --> 00:06:23.217 position:5% line:89% align:start
You two are rockin' those suits.

00:06:23.351 --> 00:06:25.086 position:13% line:89% align:start
That's nice of you to say.

00:06:25.319 --> 00:06:27.021 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Yeah, thanks.
-Come on!

00:06:27.154 --> 00:06:29.523 position:24% line:83% align:start
How can he say that
with a straight face?

00:06:29.657 --> 00:06:33.661 position:7% line:83% align:start
Ah! How am I supposed to follow
that?

00:06:34.394 --> 00:06:36.697 position:16% line:89% align:start
You both look very nice.

00:06:37.899 --> 00:06:39.066 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:06:40.835 --> 00:06:43.838 position:16% line:89% align:start
Um, thank you, Shinozaki.

00:06:44.305 --> 00:06:45.640 position:13% line:89% align:start
[SHINOZAKI] She covered up?

00:06:45.773 --> 00:06:48.475 position:13% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI] Why am I suddenly
so self-conscious?

00:06:48.876 --> 00:06:50.378 position:13% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI] I can't believe
we're at the pool

00:06:50.511 --> 00:06:53.547 position:10% line:83% align:start
and I'm missing out on seeing
Senpai's bathing suit.

00:06:53.848 --> 00:06:56.584 position:19% line:83% align:start
Maybe I should just ask
if she'd show it to me?

00:06:56.717 --> 00:06:59.587 position:24% line:83% align:start
No, I'm pretty sure
that constitutes harassment.

00:07:00.688 --> 00:07:02.990 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Shinozaki sighs]

00:07:03.124 --> 00:07:04.659 position:27% line:83% align:start
So, did you bring
that inner tube

00:07:04.792 --> 00:07:05.960 position:24% line:89% align:start
from home, or what?

00:07:06.093 --> 00:07:08.129 position:19% line:83% align:start
I just bought it today,
actually.

00:07:08.262 --> 00:07:09.563 position:30% line:89% align:start
You work fast.

00:07:09.764 --> 00:07:10.998 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Hayakawa chuckles]

00:07:11.332 --> 00:07:12.833 position:10% line:89% align:start
Hey! Let's go test that tube

00:07:12.967 --> 00:07:14.869 position:19% line:83% align:start
-out on the lazy river.
-I like the sound of that!

00:07:15.002 --> 00:07:16.337 position:13% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI] The lazy river?
[HAYAKAWA] Come on!

00:07:16.469 --> 00:07:17.437 position:30% line:89% align:start
[AKINA] Coming!

00:07:17.571 --> 00:07:19.140 position:33% line:89% align:start
That's right

00:07:19.273 --> 00:07:21.943 position:7% line:83% align:start
As long as we're in the water,
it's okay if I see her suit!

00:07:22.076 --> 00:07:23.144 position:27% line:89% align:start
Thanks Hayakawa!

00:07:23.277 --> 00:07:24.879 position:41% line:83% align:start
Senpai!
Let's go!

00:07:25.046 --> 00:07:27.081 position:27% line:83% align:start
You can all go on
and have fun.

00:07:27.214 --> 00:07:28.549 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:07:29.283 --> 00:07:32.620 position:13% line:83% align:start
She must really not want me
to look at her.

00:07:32.987 --> 00:07:35.488 position:30% line:83% align:start
The problem is
that I can't swim!

00:07:35.623 --> 00:07:37.692 position:21% line:83% align:start
How about we try out
the wave pool.

00:07:37.825 --> 00:07:39.360 position:21% line:89% align:start
You can all go ahead.

00:07:39.492 --> 00:07:40.962 position:16% line:89% align:start
I meant the kiddie pool?

00:07:41.095 --> 00:07:42.129 position:33% line:89% align:start
Go on ahead.

00:07:42.263 --> 00:07:43.564 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chuckles]

00:07:44.598 --> 00:07:45.900 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:07:46.200 --> 00:07:47.467 position:41% line:89% align:start
Hmm...

00:07:48.369 --> 00:07:49.537 position:44% line:89% align:start
Uh...

00:07:49.804 --> 00:07:53.207 position:19% line:83% align:start
Senpai, you don't know
how to swim, do you?

00:07:55.142 --> 00:07:56.277 position:44% line:89% align:start
Mm...

00:07:56.844 --> 00:07:58.478 position:13% line:89% align:start
It's not that I can't swim!

00:07:58.612 --> 00:08:00.114 position:30% line:83% align:start
It's just that
I never have before!

00:08:00.247 --> 00:08:02.917 position:7% line:83% align:start
Kay, then that basically means
you can't swim.

00:08:06.520 --> 00:08:07.755 position:41% line:89% align:start
Hmm...

00:08:07.922 --> 00:08:10.490 position:21% line:83% align:start
I shouldn't make fun!
I'm sorry, Senpai!

00:08:10.624 --> 00:08:11.559 position:30% line:89% align:start
[boy laughing]

00:08:11.692 --> 00:08:13.160 position:10% line:89% align:start
Mommy, can we get ice cream?

00:08:13.294 --> 00:08:14.762 position:19% line:83% align:start
-Well, why don't we ask
your dad? -When I was little

00:08:14.895 --> 00:08:16.931 position:16% line:83% align:start
I went into the deep end
and lost my footing.

00:08:17.064 --> 00:08:20.034 position:13% line:83% align:start
[water gurgling] I could've
very easily drowned that day

00:08:20.835 --> 00:08:23.504 position:13% line:83% align:start
and I've been afraid of it
ever since.

00:08:23.871 --> 00:08:27.575 position:33% line:83% align:start
I do think it
would be fun and all, but...

00:08:27.708 --> 00:08:29.043 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:08:29.844 --> 00:08:32.513 position:16% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI] In that case,
wanna go in together?

00:08:32.646 --> 00:08:34.048 position:44% line:89% align:start
Uh...

00:08:34.215 --> 00:08:36.884 position:13% line:83% align:start
I'm tall enough that I can
stand up in the deep end.

00:08:37.018 --> 00:08:39.153 position:7% line:83% align:start
We'll watch out for each other,
okay?

00:08:41.455 --> 00:08:43.057 position:41% line:89% align:start
Huh...

00:08:43.657 --> 00:08:44.692 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hm...

00:08:45.026 --> 00:08:47.528 position:27% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI] Alright!
I'll give it a try.

00:08:49.930 --> 00:08:53.034 position:19% line:83% align:start
Hey, it isn't as chilly
as I thought it would be.

00:08:53.334 --> 00:08:55.136 position:10% line:89% align:start
Not so scary after all, huh?

00:08:55.269 --> 00:08:56.337 position:44% line:89% align:start
Nope!

00:08:56.637 --> 00:08:57.972 position:13% line:89% align:start
In fact, I almost feel like

00:08:58.105 --> 00:09:00.641 position:35% line:83% align:start
I can start
swimming now!

00:09:02.276 --> 00:09:04.378 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Ahh...
-Huh?

00:09:04.678 --> 00:09:06.547 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI]
What's the matter, Shinozaki?

00:09:06.680 --> 00:09:07.848 position:38% line:89% align:start
Nothing.

00:09:07.982 --> 00:09:09.750 position:33% line:83% align:start
I must resist
any dirty thoughts!

00:09:09.884 --> 00:09:12.019 position:10% line:89% align:start
My Senpai is trying her best!

00:09:12.153 --> 00:09:16.123 position:27% line:83% align:start
So, are you ready
to teach me how to swim?

00:09:16.257 --> 00:09:18.225 position:30% line:89% align:start
I'm in danger.

00:09:18.726 --> 00:09:19.960 position:19% line:89% align:start
Let's start off small.

00:09:20.094 --> 00:09:21.829 position:21% line:83% align:start
Try putting your face
in the water.

00:09:21.962 --> 00:09:26.100 position:10% line:83% align:start
Easy-peasy! Leave it to me-z!
Here I go then!

00:09:27.502 --> 00:09:30.638 position:19% line:83% align:start
Huh, she might actually
pick it up quickly.

00:09:31.038 --> 00:09:32.807 position:38% line:89% align:start
[whines]

00:09:32.973 --> 00:09:34.408 position:24% line:89% align:start
[SHINOZAKI] Or not.

00:09:34.543 --> 00:09:37.311 position:13% line:83% align:start
Normally, I can put my face
underwater with no issue.

00:09:37.445 --> 00:09:38.846 position:33% line:89% align:start
Why not now?

00:09:39.180 --> 00:09:41.715 position:5% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI] You might be nervous
because of where we are.

00:09:41.982 --> 00:09:43.584 position:21% line:83% align:start
