You can go ahead
without me if you want.

00:17:54.676 --> 00:17:56.578 position:30% line:83% align:start
Take your time.
I don't mind waiting.

00:17:56.711 --> 00:17:58.780 position:10% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI] I mind very much,
thank you!

00:17:58.913 --> 00:17:59.781 position:35% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI]
Achoo!

00:17:59.914 --> 00:18:00.848 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Oh!
-Huh?

00:18:01.214 --> 00:18:02.349 position:35% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI]
Crap.

00:18:02.482 --> 00:18:03.785 position:35% line:83% align:start
[HAYAKAWA]
Did you say something?

00:18:03.918 --> 00:18:05.553 position:27% line:83% align:start
-[AKINA] Not me.
-[HAYAKAWA] I could have sworn

00:18:05.687 --> 00:18:06.888 position:27% line:89% align:start
I heard a voice.

00:18:07.021 --> 00:18:08.422 position:10% line:83% align:start
-[AKINA] From outside, maybe?
-[Shiori sighs]

00:18:08.556 --> 00:18:10.290 position:35% line:83% align:start
[HAYAKAWA]
I think it came from the closet.

00:18:10.424 --> 00:18:12.927 position:35% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI]
No, no, no!

00:18:13.193 --> 00:18:14.762 position:30% line:83% align:start
-[SHIORI] Oh...
-[SHINOZAKI] Huh?

00:18:14.929 --> 00:18:16.163 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI]
Hm.

00:18:16.931 --> 00:18:18.198 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chuckles]

00:18:19.067 --> 00:18:20.434 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:18:21.268 --> 00:18:23.838 position:16% line:83% align:start
It's your special Senpai
heating pad!

00:18:23.972 --> 00:18:25.506 position:33% line:89% align:start
Um, my what?

00:18:25.707 --> 00:18:27.307 position:27% line:89% align:start
Is it super warm?

00:18:27.441 --> 00:18:29.343 position:35% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI]
Yeah, it sure is.

00:18:29.476 --> 00:18:31.311 position:7% line:89% align:start
Wait, did you say heating pad?

00:18:31.512 --> 00:18:33.548 position:44% line:83% align:start
Yup.
I mean, you're sneezing.

00:18:33.681 --> 00:18:35.683 position:10% line:83% align:start
- Gaah! - That means you need
to be warmed up!

00:18:35.817 --> 00:18:39.319 position:16% line:83% align:start
Huh? It really is coming
from in there.

00:18:39.621 --> 00:18:41.589 position:35% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI]
Guh! Busted.

00:18:42.023 --> 00:18:43.658 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI]
Your Senpai heating pad!

00:18:43.791 --> 00:18:46.193 position:7% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI] Please, cut it out.
This isn't the time for that!

00:18:46.326 --> 00:18:48.228 position:27% line:83% align:start
They're gonna get
the wrong idea!

00:18:48.362 --> 00:18:50.965 position:19% line:83% align:start
Well, this heating pad
is the adhesive kind!

00:18:51.099 --> 00:18:52.466 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmmm!

00:18:53.034 --> 00:18:54.702 position:5% line:83% align:start
-[SHINOZAKI] Oh crap, oh crap...
-[SHIORI] Aren't you comfy?

00:18:54.836 --> 00:18:56.104 position:38% line:89% align:start
Oh crap!

00:18:56.236 --> 00:18:57.204 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Shiori giggles]

00:18:57.839 --> 00:18:59.874 position:33% line:83% align:start
Look, Senpai.
Sorry to be rude,

00:19:00.008 --> 00:19:02.043 position:13% line:83% align:start
but you have to quiet down
for a second.

00:19:02.175 --> 00:19:02.977 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:19:03.111 --> 00:19:04.112 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh.

00:19:04.579 --> 00:19:06.914 position:10% line:83% align:start
Maybe you were just imagining
things.

00:19:07.048 --> 00:19:08.181 position:27% line:89% align:start
Yeah, I guess so.

00:19:08.348 --> 00:19:09.449 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:19:09.817 --> 00:19:11.886 position:35% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI]
Barely avoided disaster.

00:19:12.319 --> 00:19:14.522 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Shinozaki.
-Huh?

00:19:14.822 --> 00:19:16.189 position:35% line:89% align:start
Your hand,

00:19:16.824 --> 00:19:18.026 position:27% line:89% align:start
it's on my, um...

00:19:18.158 --> 00:19:19.894 position:38% line:89% align:start
[screams]

00:19:20.028 --> 00:19:20.928 position:41% line:89% align:start
[thud]

00:19:21.062 --> 00:19:22.229 position:35% line:89% align:start
[both gasp]

00:19:22.730 --> 00:19:25.399 position:24% line:83% align:start
-Did you hear that?
-I did.

00:19:25.967 --> 00:19:28.736 position:21% line:83% align:start
Come to think of it,
this place does have a history.

00:19:28.870 --> 00:19:30.104 position:21% line:89% align:start
Don't even go there!

00:19:30.237 --> 00:19:34.408 position:19% line:83% align:start
Please, we were having
so much fun together, and now...

00:19:34.609 --> 00:19:35.342 position:38% line:89% align:start
[shrieks]

00:19:35.610 --> 00:19:37.578 position:7% line:89% align:start
Wait, if there are ghosts here,

00:19:37.712 --> 00:19:40.048 position:19% line:83% align:start
do you think those two
got spirited away?

00:19:40.715 --> 00:19:42.650 position:13% line:89% align:start
Well, we can't rule it out.

00:19:42.784 --> 00:19:44.552 position:5% line:83% align:start
[HAYAKAWA] What are we gonna do?
Call the police?

00:19:44.686 --> 00:19:47.287 position:27% line:83% align:start
Call an exorcist?
Call the police and an exorcist?

00:19:47.421 --> 00:19:48.956 position:10% line:83% align:start
-[AKINA] Stay calm, Hayakawa!
-[Hayakawa cries]

00:19:49.090 --> 00:19:50.158 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:19:50.290 --> 00:19:53.761 position:33% line:83% align:start
Who is that?
Hayakawa maybe?

00:19:54.128 --> 00:19:55.697 position:16% line:89% align:start
We're here in the closet!

00:19:55.830 --> 00:19:57.565 position:13% line:83% align:start
I wanna go to the open-air
bath too.

00:19:57.699 --> 00:19:59.000 position:13% line:89% align:start
[SHINOZAKI] Ahh! Be quiet!

00:19:59.133 --> 00:20:00.333 position:10% line:89% align:start
You're gonna blow our cover!

00:20:00.467 --> 00:20:03.971 position:10% line:83% align:start
Come on, think of a solution!
Gah!

00:20:04.271 --> 00:20:06.206 position:24% line:83% align:start
-[door slides open]
-Huh? -Huh?

00:20:06.406 --> 00:20:10.712 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Hayakawa.
-[scream]

00:20:11.145 --> 00:20:14.448 position:10% line:83% align:start
[eerie voice] Huh? Who turned
out the lights in here?

00:20:14.582 --> 00:20:15.983 position:16% line:83% align:start
[HAYAKAWA] Don't kill me!
Please!

00:20:16.117 --> 00:20:19.120 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Stay away!
-[AKINA] Wait for me! Hayakawa!

00:20:19.687 --> 00:20:22.590 position:21% line:83% align:start
Wow, I can't believe
they didn't figure us out.

00:20:22.724 --> 00:20:23.524 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ah?!

00:20:23.658 --> 00:20:24.992 position:41% line:89% align:start
Huh...

00:20:25.325 --> 00:20:26.794 position:33% line:89% align:start
She's asleep.

00:20:27.662 --> 00:20:29.797 position:13% line:89% align:start
I guess the chaos is over.

00:20:30.064 --> 00:20:31.165 position:38% line:89% align:start
For now.

00:20:31.866 --> 00:20:36.771 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'm getting kinda tired.
Are you okay, Shinozaki?

00:20:37.138 --> 00:20:38.238 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chuckles]

00:20:38.840 --> 00:20:41.308 position:5% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI] Senpai, you'll get a
cold if you sleep there.

00:20:41.441 --> 00:20:42.777 position:21% line:89% align:start
Let's put you to bed.

00:20:42.944 --> 00:20:44.812 position:44% line:89% align:start
Okay.

00:20:49.016 --> 00:20:51.586 position:30% line:83% align:start
She was worried
about how she came across,

00:20:52.252 --> 00:20:55.422 position:13% line:83% align:start
but I'm happy I got to see
a different side of her.

00:20:58.092 --> 00:20:59.527 position:41% line:89% align:start
Uh-uh.

00:21:00.795 --> 00:21:01.963 position:35% line:89% align:start
Her hands.

00:21:02.196 --> 00:21:05.365 position:33% line:83% align:start
Come on now.
Let me go.

00:21:06.000 --> 00:21:07.568 position:27% line:89% align:start
I can't get away.

00:21:07.702 --> 00:21:10.437 position:19% line:83% align:start
Oh boy, this might look
worse than before!

00:21:10.638 --> 00:21:12.607 position:10% line:83% align:start
[running footsteps] [panting]
[HAYAKAWA] This way!

00:21:12.774 --> 00:21:14.742 position:13% line:89% align:start
I saw a ghost in this room!

00:21:14.876 --> 00:21:15.977 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gaping]

00:21:16.110 --> 00:21:17.111 position:38% line:89% align:start
[exhales]

00:21:17.344 --> 00:21:19.580 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whimpers]

00:21:22.817 --> 00:21:24.417 position:13% line:89% align:start
Time to prepare the feast.

00:21:24.552 --> 00:21:26.521 position:10% line:83% align:start
-We've got big news, Yutaka!
-[YUTAKA] I see

00:21:26.654 --> 00:21:28.956 position:24% line:83% align:start
-the wedding is on.
-Absolutely not!

00:21:29.090 --> 00:21:30.758 position:5% line:89% align:start
[AKINA] Oh, what a glorious day!

00:21:30.892 --> 00:21:32.492 position:35% line:83% align:start
[HAYAKAWA]
Wait, where's the ghost?

00:21:32.627 --> 00:21:34.028 position:10% line:83% align:start
[HAYAKAWA] I swear it was in
here howling at me!

00:21:34.162 --> 00:21:36.264 position:21% line:89% align:start
[overlapping chatter]

00:21:36.396 --> 00:21:37.598 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:21:37.732 --> 00:21:40.300 position:13% line:89% align:start
This place is a lot of fun.

